证据片段: A second set of specimens was therefore irradiated for nine months at 262°C in the NRU reactor at Chalk River Nuclear Laboratories (CRNL)

证据片段: Sixteen curved compact specimens were spark machined from the failed P2-G16 pressure tube and tested as part of the failure analysis program. These contained hydrides, in concentrations ranging from 42 to 146 μg/g, in mixed orientations (i.e., both circumferential and radial hydrides were present)

文献ID: STP939-EB-Zirconium in the Nuclear Industry_7th Volume_044_chunk3

证据片段: Brittle behavior was observed for two conditions. Some specimens containing 100 μg/g or more circumferential hydride, and tested at 25°C, failed in this manner

证据片段: An experimental program undertaken by CEA, EDF, and FRAGEMA with the aim of characterizing the fatigue and creep-fatigue behavior of Zircaloy-4 following different annealing treatments (recrystallization, stress relief, etc.) is in progress.
